query:
INSERT INTO reminder (
            application_id,
            interaction_id,
            note_id,
            job_listing_id,
            company_id,
            person_id,
            reminder_date,
            title,
            message,
            is_completed
        )
        VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)
        RETURNING
            id AS "id!: i64",
            application_id,
            interaction_id,
            note_id,
            job_listing_id,
            company_id,
            person_id,
            reminder_date AS "reminder_date!: NaiveDate",
            title AS "title!: String",
            message,
            is_completed as "is_completed!: bool",
            created_at AS "created_at!: NaiveDateTime",
            updated_at AS "updated_at!: NaiveDateTime"
